  <brief_title>The Glycaemic Effects of Glucerna® in Critically Ill Patients.</brief_title>
  <acronym>GluCip</acronym>
  <official_title>Glucerna in Critically Ill Patients (GluCip Trial): Investigating the Glycaemic Effects of a Reduced-carbohydrate, Modified-fat, Fiber-containing Enteral Formula (Glucerna®) in Critically Ill Patients.</official_title>
